OL,10,FWhat is vitamin B12?
OL,12,FB12 is a vitamin naturally found in
OL,13,Fanimal products but it can also be
OL,14,Fadded to foods.
OL,16,FThe vitamin is important for the
OL,17,Ffunctioning of your nerves and the
OL,18,Fproduction of DNA in your cells.
