OL,3,CWhat is vitamin B12 and are you
OL,4,Cdeficient?
OL,6,FB12 also works with folic acid to make
OL,7,Fred blood cells and other compounds
OL,8,Fthat are needed for the cardiovascular
OL,9,Fand immune systems to work properly.
