OL,3,CWhat is vitamin B12 and are you
OL,4,Cdeficient?
OL,6,FHow is B12 deficiency diagnosed?
OL,8,FIf a doctor suspects somebody may be
OL,9,Fdeficient in B12 based on the list of
OL,10,Fsymptoms, they will recommend a series
OL,11,Fof initial tests.
OL,13,FThis will typically involve blood
OL,14,Ftests that look at the level of B12 in
OL,15,Fyour blood, as well as whether you
OL,16,Fhave healthy levels of haemoglobin
OL,17,F(the substance that transports oxygen
OL,18,Faround the body) and how much folate
OL,19,F(or folic acid) is in your blood.
