OL,3,CWhat is vitamin B12 and are you
OL,4,Cdeficient?
OL,6,FIf the deficiency is caused by diet,
OL,7,Fmedical professionals may suggest
OL,8,Ftaking vitamin B12 tablets in between
OL,9,Fmeals and eating more vitamin B12-rich
OL,10,Ffoods.
OL,12,FShould I get tested for B12 deficiency?
OL,14,FNew guidance suggests that if a
OL,15,Fpatient has at least one common
OL,16,Fsymptom of B12 deficiency and one
OL,17,Fcommon risk factor, they should be
OL,18,Foffered an initial diagnostic test.
